Title: Turn, Turn, Turn
Plot: When the CSIs are called to a murder scene at a familiar motel, Nick is thrown for a loop as he pieces together three separate murder investigations that all took place at the same establishment over the course of a year.
GuestStars: Archie Kao, Taylor Swift, Alex Carter, Sheeri Rappaport, Jon Wellner, Larry Mitchell, Alessandra Torresani, Stephen Heath, Geoffrey Blake, Lisa Darr
